        <p>• <strong>软件框架</strong>：PyTorch 2.0, CUDA 11.8, Python 3.10, Transformers 4.30</p>
        <p>• <strong>训练配置</strong>：Batch Size 64, Learning Rate 1e-4 (cosine decay), Epochs 100, AdamW optimizer</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
